    {
      "name": "CatalogueToExtendedCrateCodecError",
      "description": "Error type for the Catalogue -> ExtendedCrate (TypeGraph A) codec. Variants: InvalidTypeRef { type_ref: String, reason: String } (syn parse failed; struct variant carrying the offending TypeRef and a reason string) / AmbiguousIdentifier { name: String } (short name collision; struct variant carrying the conflicting name). Crate-prefixed TypeRef values are auto-collected into external_crates and never rejected (ADR 2 D5 / D11 open-world semantics); ExternalCrateUnresolvable is not a valid codec error.",
